  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，我发现了基地的一些情况，我们追踪到山顶雷达站发出了奇怪的信号。那些信号非常诡异，我怀疑不是好事。\n\n你能过去在大圆顶内顶部放一个信号干扰器吗？\n既然都要去，我建议你也装个摄像头，我想看看都是什么人在出入那个雷达站。",
    "en": "Hey I found out something about the base, we traced weird signals from the radar station on the hill. Those were really weird signals, I doubt it's something good.\n\nCan you head there and place down a signal jammer? Right at the top inside the dome.\nWhile you're there I suggest you set up a camera there aswell, I want to see what kind of people visit that station."
  },
